<img src="https://www.savethestudent.org/uploads/Tom-Allingham-Author-Profile-100x100.jpg" height="75" width="75" alt="Tom Allingham" class="profile-image" loading="eager" />
</div>
<div class="meta">
<h2>WRITTEN BY Tom Allingham</h2>
<p>Tom joined Save the Student in 2017, initially heading up the editorial team before becoming Communications Director. He has appeared as a Student Finance expert on a range of TV and radio stations including the BBC, ITV and Sky, sharing his top tips for saving money and cutting student bills.
<br/><a href="https://www.savethestudent.org/author/tom-allingham">Read more</a></p>
